葡萄柚富有[[維他命C|維他命C]]、[[果膠|果膠]]及[[番茄紅素|番茄紅素]]<ref name="WHF"/>。每100克的葡萄柚帶有維他命C[[參考每日攝入量|參考每日攝入量]]的兩成以上<ref name="WHF"/>。有研究指出葡萄柚能夠降低體內[[膽固醇|膽固醇]]<ref name="WHF"/>，其種子亦有抗氧化成份。<ref name="Extract">{{cite journal |vauthors=Armando C, Maythe S, Beatriz NP |title=Antioxidant activity of grapefruit seed extract on vegetable oils |journal=J Sci Food Agric. |volume=77 |issue=4 |pages=463–7 |year=1997 |url=http://www3.interscience.wiley.com/cgi-bin/abstract/10007270/ABSTRACT |doi=10.1002/(SICI)1097-0010(199808)77:4<463::AID-JSFA62>3.0.CO;2-1 |access-date=2017-12-27 |archive-date=2012-12-16 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20121216134233/http://www3.interscience.wiley.com/cgi-bin/abstract/10007270/ABSTRACT |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。由於葡萄柚的[[升糖指數|升糖指數]]較低，以葡萄柚作主要元素的[[葡萄柚飲食法|葡萄柚飲食法]]被指能夠協助[[代謝|代謝]]系統燃脂。<ref name="Grapefruit_Diet">WMUR Ch. 9: New Hampshire news, weather, sports and entertainment. Researchers Put Grapefruit Diet To Test: Grapefruit Compound Lowers Cholesterol, Helps Regulate Insulin. June 11, 2003. [http://www.wmur.com/health/2262919/detail.html Article] {{Wayback|url=http://www.wmur.com/health/2262919/detail.html |date=20070528055724 }}</ref>

[[葡萄柚籽精華素|葡萄柚籽精華素]]被某些廠商宣傳為天然的[[防腐劑|防腐劑]]，但研究指出其抗菌特性實際上來自[[对羟基苯甲酸酯|对羟基苯甲酸酯]]等合成防腐劑對種子原料的污染。<ref name="Study">{{cite journal |vauthors=Sakamoto S, Sato K, Maitani T, Yamada T |title=[Analysis of components in natural food additive "grapefruit seed extract" by HPLC and LC/MS] |language=ja |journal=Eisei Shikenjo Hokoku |issue=114 |pages=38–42 |year=1996 |pmid=9037863}}</ref><ref name="Pharmazie">{{cite journal |vauthors=von Woedtke T, Schlüter B, Pflegel P, Lindequist U, Jülich WD |title=Aspects of the antimicrobial efficacy of grapefruit seed extract and its relation to preservative substances contained |journal=Pharmazie |volume=54 |issue=6 |pages=452–6 |date=June 1999 |pmid=10399191}}</ref><ref name="Contamination">{{cite journal |vauthors=Takeoka G, Dao L, Wong RY, Lundin R, Mahoney N |title=Identification of benzethonium chloride in commercial grapefruit seed extracts |journal=J. Agric. Food Chem. |volume=49 |issue=7 |pages=3316–20 |date=July 2001 |pmid=11453769 |doi=10.1021/jf010222w}}</ref><ref name="Adulteration">{{cite journal |vauthors=Takeoka GR, Dao LT, Wong RY, Harden LA |title=Identification of benzalkonium chloride in commercial grapefruit seed extracts |journal=J. Agric. Food Chem. |volume=53 |issue=19 |pages=7630–6 |date=September 2005 |pmid=16159196 |doi=10.1021/jf0514064}}</ref><ref name="Preservatives">{{cite journal |vauthors=Ganzera M, Aberham A, Stuppner H |title=Development and validation of an HPLC/UV/MS method for simultaneous determination of 18 preservatives in grapefruit seed extract |journal=J. Agric. Food Chem. |volume=54 |issue=11 |pages=3768–72 |date=May 2006 |pmid=16719494 |doi=10.1021/jf060543d}}</ref>

==禁忌==
*葡萄柚會加強或抵銷許多常見藥物（如心血管用藥、降血脂藥物、[[抗組織胺藥|抗組織胺藥]]、 [[器官移植|器官移植]]抗-{排}-斥藥等）的作用，讓藥物在人體內積存而使濃度增加及滯留時間延長，就像服藥過量一般，藥物從有益變成有害，導致容易產生副作用，嚴重時甚至會造成死亡。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www2.edah.org.tw/ph/pub/%E8%97%A5%E7%89%A9%E8%88%87%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9/3.%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E8%97%A5%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E8%88%87%E8%91%A1%E8%90%84%E6%9F%9A%E6%B1%81%E4%B8%80%E8%B5%B7%E6%9C%8D%E7%94%A8.pdf |title=哪些药不可与葡萄柚汁一起服用 |accessdate=2016-07-06 |archive-date=2016-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161011005321/http://www2.edah.org.tw/ph/pub/%E8%97%A5%E7%89%A9%E8%88%87%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9/3.%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E8%97%A5%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E8%88%87%E8%91%A1%E8%90%84%E6%9F%9A%E6%B1%81%E4%B8%80%E8%B5%B7%E6%9C%8D%E7%94%A8.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://homepage.vghtpe.gov.tw/~pharm/drug-sense/D9.htm |title=致命危機：當葡萄柚與藥共舞! |access-date=2016-07-06 |archive-date=2016-07-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160720174751/http://homepage.vghtpe.gov.tw/~pharm/drug-sense/D9.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>西柚不能与药同时吃，间隔最好在24小时以上。
*并不是所有的[[柚子|柚子]]，只有葡萄柚在与部分药物同服时才会引起不良反应。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/food/2015-11/20/c_1117202051.htm |title=南京日报：网传“药物和柚子同吃等于服毒” 西柚可能影响药效 |access-date=2016-07-06 |archive-date=2017-11-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171123132946/http://news.xinhuanet.com/food/2015-11/20/c_1117202051.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==历史==
18世纪在[[巴巴多斯|巴巴多斯]]首次杂交培育。<ref name="Carrington & Fraser">{{cite book |last1=Carrington |first1=Sean |last2=Fraser |first2=HenryC |title=A~Z of Barbados Heritage |accessdate=6 April 2010 |edition= |series= |volume= |date= |year=2003 |month= |origyear= |publisher=Macmillan Caribbean |location= |isbn=0333920686 |pages=90–91 |chapter=Grapefruit }}</ref>它曾与同为[[柑橘属|柑橘属]]的[[柚子|柚子]]被混为一类。19世纪后期这种水果开始受人欢迎，之前只是一种装饰性植物。美国很快成为主要生产国，在[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]，[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]，[[亚利桑那州|亚利桑那州]]，和[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]]均有种植。中国在20世纪初引进。

== 生產 ==
[[File:2005grapefruit_and_pomelo.PNG|thumb]]的各國產量]]
[[美國|美國]]是世界最大的葡萄柚與柚子的生產國，而[[中國|中國]]、[[南非|南非]]分居二、三位。

